Manual Testing Documentation - Brew & Bean Café
Project Overview
Brew & Bean Café is a fictional coffee shop website created as part of a web development project. The purpose of this website is to establish an inviting and professional online presence for the café, serving as the primary destination where visitors can explore the café's story, view the coffee menu, and get in touch for bookings or inquiries.

The Brew & Bean Café website is currently live at: https://brew-bean-cafe-bpm8umlm6-abdell-abdellas-projects.vercel.app/

