Issues Found & Resolutions
Issue 1: CSS !important Overuse
Problem: Excessive use of !important declarations in initial CSS
Resolution: Removed all unnecessary !important declarations and improved selector specificity

Issue 2: W3C Validation Error
Problem: Validator couldn't access local CSS file
Resolution: Used "By Direct Input" validation method and added type="text/css" to link tags

Issue 3: Missing Form Action
Problem: Contact form lacked action attribute in initial version
Resolution: Added proper form handling and JavaScript validation

Issue 4: Image Responsiveness
Problem: Some images didn't scale properly on mobile
Resolution: Added max-width: 100% and height: auto to all images

Issue 5: Navigation on Mobile
Problem: Navigation menu didn't collapse properly on small screens
Resolution: Implemented media queries for mobile navigation

